description: WebRetro is a web development hackathon that challenges participants to create web applications using retro-inspired designs and technologies. This hackathon is a great opportunity for participants to showcase their creativity and web development skills while building interactive and engaging web experiences with a nostalgic twist.

CodeCraft is a web development hackathon that challenges participants to develop innovative web applications using modern web technologies such as React, node.js, and others. This hackathon is a great opportunity for participants to showcase their web development skills and creativity while building interactive and engaging web experiences.
Algo-thon is a DSA competition where you can test your skills and compete with other participants.
